			<h1>History of BAYADA Home Health Care</h1>
			<!--<img class='bhistory-logo' src="/images/logos/40th_anniversary_logo_website.png" width="567" height="75" alt="Bayada logo">-->
			<h2 class='italics'>Helping people has been - and will always be - our singular purpose. It is the driving force behind <span class="italics">The BAYADA Way</span>, our company philosophy, and the heart of everything we do.</h2><br>
			<a onclick="ga('send', {
				hitType: 'event',
				eventCategory: 'Bayada History Ebook',
