				eventLabel: 'Bayada History'
			  });" href="/upload/BAYADA1_112HiResSingleBlank_low res.pdf" target="_blank"><span class="hidden">link opens in new window</span><img class='book-cta' src="/images/cta/ebook_graphic.jpg" alt="read the ebook of the bayada way history book"/></a>

			<p>The origins of BAYADA Home Health Care date back to 1975, when J. Mark Baiada opened his first office in Philadelphia, PA, with a vision that everyone should be entitled to a safe home life, with comfort, independence, and dignity. Mark always felt a higher sense of purpose toward his clients, and he believed that when you entered someone's home, you entered their lives. Finding like-minded professionals with the same sense of purpose and passion for helping others has been the foundation of our work and the more Mark found, the more the company grew.</p>

			<p>Four decades later, BAYADA has made the unprecedented transition to a not for profit organization, and grown from those humble beginnings to become a national leader in the home care industry, with more than 347 service offices in 22 states, with locations in Germany, India, Ireland, New Zealand, United Kingdom, Canada and South Korea.</p>

			<p>Today, BAYADA provides the highest quality care in the home to children and adults of all ages, spanning every level of care&mdash;from complex, high-tech care to just being there. Every day in every home, that care is delivered with compassion, excellence, and reliability &ndash; our BAYADA core values.</p>

			<p>To learn more about our history, click on the BAYADA <a href="images/BAYADA-History-Timeline.pdf" target="_blank"><span class="hidden">link opens in new window</span> timeline</a> below. Please also enjoy the free electronic version of our company’s history book, <a href='https://www.bayada.com/history-book' target="_blank"><span class="hidden">link opens in new window</span><span class='italics'>BAYADA: 40 Years of Compassion, Excellence, and Reliability</span></a>. <!-- Hardback copies of our book are available for purchase on <a href='http://www.amazon.com/BAYADA-Years-Compassion-Excellence-Reliability/dp/0990601226/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1439395719&sr=8-1&keywords=bayada' target="_blank"><span class="hidden">link opens in new window</span>Amazon.com</a>. -->
			</p>

